<br>
higher level pvp, when everyone has <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> resist gear</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and when your pet is pathetic vs higher level, high ac melees, you would see mages do have real problems.<br>
<br>
1) NO low resist way to do damage. all our nukes are slow casting and easily resistable. in pve this is not much of a problem, but in pvp it is.<br>
<br>
2) NO way to heal ourselves or mitigate damage aside from pet. again, this is not a problem in pve since most mobs are stupid enough to let our pet tank, unfortunately players are a just a wee bit smarter. <br>
<br>
